ON MARCH 1st 2023 AVENUE BEAUTY BOUTIQUE CELEBRATED ITS 10 YEAR ANNIVERSARY!
 
Wow a whole decade full of beauty, life, love, happiness, stress, laughter, tears, accomplishments, goals, hard work, friendships, families, employees, 1000’s of brides and 1000’s of clients. I have never been so proud and excited.
 
I definitely didn’t get here overnight.
 I was 15 years old when I moved to the U.S., my story is similar to many others, I came here as a refugee with my family, uncertain as what to expect when it came to my future. So, I decided to take control of my future and destiny. Throughout many years of dedication, hard work, determination, trials and tribulations, I build a successful styling-beauty empire, one which is expanding and flourishing, and will continue to do so for many years to come.
My success and experience allowed me to help many others, educate them and help them built their own paths. I did all this with passion, dedication, and a great support system behind me. I will never forget the people who guided me, and mentored me through this journey. So many people inspired me and gave me the greatest advice. Thank you , @virginiasav , @sedaesmaili_hairstylist I worked along with these amazing talented stylists and they guided me through my career and I built strong work ethics and experience.
 
Thank you to my parents, my brother, my husband, my friends and my clients. If it wasn’t for your support, I’m not sure where I’d be here today. And a special thank you to my husband. I truly believe you are my Lucky Star. After meeting you, so many doors have opened up for me, not just in my career, but life in general. Thank you to my son Vinny for pushing me harder to be the best and provide the best future for him and our family. 
 
And to all my clients near, far, new, old, thank you for believing in me and continuing to support me and my small business. I appreciate every single one of you. 
 
LOVE ARSINEH…

🤍🤍🤍 BRIDAL HAIR TRIAL 🤍🤍🤍

They say less is more and I agree. Loving this simple bridal hair style. You can accessorize it with a crown or just a simple pin or non. 
BRIDAL HAIR TRIAL INFORMATION: All bridal hair trials are done on weekdays. Service is anywhere from 2 to 3 hours. I offer 2 to 3 different hair styles that I create from start to finish. Here are a few tips when booking a bridal hair trial.
•wash your hair the night before
•wear something white to resemble your wedding gown
•do a makeup trial before your hair/do your own makeup, that way you see the full results after your hair is done
•have some inspirational photos ready 
•have fun!!!
For more bridal hair service such as trials, consultations and day of wedding you can contact me at 818-606-5141 or email at avenuebeautyla@gmail.com
